玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama) 成为 2024 年全英音乐奖新任主持人https://www.nme.com/news/music/maya-jama-among-the-new-hosts-for-the-brit-awards-2024-3581190?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=maya-jama-among- 2024 年全英音乐奖新东道主Liberty DunworthFri, 02 Feb 2024 10:15:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsBRIT Awards https://www.nme.com/?p=3581190 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama) 出席 2023 年时尚大奖" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>新公告是在莫·吉利根 (Mo Gilligan) 离职后发布的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/maya-jama-among-the-new-hosts-for-the-brit-awards-2024-3581190">2024 年全英音乐奖新任主持人之一的玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama)</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛雅·贾玛 (Maya Jama) 出席 2023 年时尚大奖" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Maya-Jama@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">全英音乐奖</a>的组织者宣布了 2024 年颁奖典礼的新主办方。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2023-winners-list-3396601">以下是 2023 年全英音乐奖的所有获奖者</a></strong></li></ul><p>新的颁奖团队是在过去两年主持颁奖典礼的前主持人莫吉利根(Mo Gilligan)离开后出现的。</p><p>他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mo-gilligan-to-step-down-and-hand-over-the-baton-as-brit-awards-host-3549693">宣布他不会回来演出今年的演出</a>，并确认这与他在美国的巡演承诺相冲突。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mo-gilligan-to-host-2022-brit-awards-as-gendered-awards-scrapped-3101713">他于 2022 年接替喜剧演员杰克·怀特霍尔 (Jack Whitehall) 担任该角色</a>，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mo-gilligan-returning-to-host-2023-brit-awards-3377776">于次年重返该职位。</a></p><p>现在，这项享有盛誉的音乐盛会的组织者似乎在 2024 年采取了不同的方式，今年将由三位主持人而不是通常的一位主持人来主持。</p><p>其中包括英国电视节目主持人兼电台 DJ Maya Jama，她因与 BBC Radio 1 的合作而广受认可，并且是热门英国真人秀<em>《Love Island》</em>的最新主持人。她还主持了去年与吉利根的部分节目</p><p>与她一起的还有电视节目主持人兼 BBC Radio 1 主持人 Clara Amfo（截至去年 12 月，她连续两年主持<em>Future Sounds</em> ）以及<em>The One Show</em>和 Capital FM 的主持人 Roman Kemp。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C20dDF-oRwD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div>